sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant C as Client
  participant G as API Gateway
  participant U as Upstream Contract
  participant B as banking-admin

  C->>G: GET /api/v1/balances?account_id&asset_code
  G->>G: auth boundary check
  G->>G: resolve correlation id
  G->>U: listBalances(filters, correlation_id)
  U->>B: GET /banking_admin/api/v1/balances?...

  alt success
    B-->>U: 200 balances payload
    U-->>G: 200 balances payload
    G-->>C: 200 passthrough payload
  else upstream failure
    U-->>G: transport/protocol failure
    G-->>C: 503 upstream_unavailable
  end
